== Umugambi ==
Terrick ( James Faulkner ), umupolisi w’Ubwongereza muri Afurika yepfo mu cyaro cya Rhodesia, ategereje ko umurimo we urangira ndetse n’izabukuru hakiri kare mu murima we hamwe n’umukunzi we, Sally ( Sybil Danning ). Icyizere cya Terrick cyo kubaho mu mahoro hamwe na Sally kiracika intege, ariko, igihe inyeshyamba z'abirabura b'abirabura zateye umurima. Sally yafashwe ku ngufu akicwa n'umuyobozi w'inyeshyamba, albino izwi gusa na moniker ''"Urupfu rwongorera"'' ( Horst Frank ). Ababajwe n'agahinda, Terrick n'abakozi be bo mu mirima, bayobowe na Katchemu ( Sam Williams ) bahisemo kwihorera Sally bonyine. Nyuma baza kumenya ko inyeshyamba zahamagaye abaturage baho mu nama yo kubanyapolitiki no kubateza igico "Urupfu rwongorera". Icyakora ishyaka rya Terrick rifungura umuriro imburagihe, ryica kandi rikomeretsa bamwe mu baturage bari bahari.

